Host your next event at Bar Kada, where intimate ambiance meets exceptional flavors. Our 30-seat restaurant offers a modern, stylish space perfect for gatherings of all kinds—whether you're planning a corporate event, birthday celebration, or a unique experience with friends.
Features:
Space:
Cozy, 1000 sq. ft. space with seating for up to 30 guests
Customizable Menus:
Choose from sushi-focused multi-course tastings, sushi buffets, or passed hors d'oeuvres tailored to your group’s preferences
Sake and Wine Pairings:
Enjoy curated sake and wine-based cocktails and pairings designed to elevate your event
Bento Lunch Boxes:
Perfect for a more casual, yet refined experience
Interactive Classes:
Sake and wine classes to educate and engage your guests
Tech-Friendly:
Equipped with a projector and pull-down screen for presentations or entertainment
Flexible Options:
We work with you to design the perfect menu and event format, from intimate dinners to full restaurant buyouts
Our dedicated team ensures every detail is taken care of so you can focus on enjoying the moment with your guests. Whether you’re looking for a formal tasting experience or a laid-back sushi buffet, Bar Kada is the ideal venue for creating lasting memories.
Let us host your next event—reach out today to reserve your date!
